   c. clone, compile, run, test, and modify the Software on systems controlled
      by the recipient solely to develop and maintain changes in a GitHub Fork
      or to conduct Non-Commercial Evaluation;

   d. use GitHub-hosted automation for a GitHub Fork for those same purposes;

   e. publish source changes in that GitHub Fork and submit them to the official
