   f. download, build, and run the Software solely for Non-Commercial
      Evaluation.

   These permissions are additional to any rights granted by the GitHub Terms
   of Service and do not limit rights that cannot lawfully be restricted.
   A commercial entity may exercise them solely to collaborate through the
   permitted GitHub Fork and pull-request workflow or to conduct qualifying
   internal Non-Commercial Evaluation; no other commercial right is granted.

